2 To amend and reenact R.S. 23:1553(G), to enact R.S. 49:191(3)(b), and to repeal R.S.
3 49:191(1)(f), relative to Louisiana Works, including provisions to provide for the
4 re-creation of Louisiana Works and the statutory entities made a part of the
5 department by law; to provide for the effective termination date for all statutory
6 authority for the existence of such statutory entities; to provide for the re-
7 authorization of the Incumbent Worker Training Program within Louisiana Works;
